HEADWORD: Harmonic
<hw>Har*mon"ic</hw> <pr>(h⟦aum⟧r*m⟦ocr⟧n"⟦icr⟧k)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Mus.)</fld> <def>A musical note produced by a number of vibrations
